# Description:
# 	This JSON configuration defines a Greengrass V2 component called com.greengrass.ProjectRPi4B version 1.0.0
# 	with platform-specific instructions for running the s3_test1.py script, which is stored in an S3 bucket, 
# 	and includes default configuration options and lifecycle commands for both Linux and Windows environments.
